DEPRECATED - See http://github.com/ThoughtWorksInc/InfraTraining instead, puppet folder.

This is a sample go installation with a local agent, 3 git repositories, 3 pipelines, debhelper and cucumber installed.

To use edit go.pp and set these values apropriately:

aws_access_key
aws_secret_key
aws_ami_id
aws_instance_type
go_server_deb_url
go_agent_deb_url

Then do:

sudo puppet apply --modulepath=modules go.pp
